Here you'll find most of my homelab and its utilities

If you notice something weird, thats because there's no package.json,
since one of my weird goals is to eliminate all the node_modules bloat

There will never be a express server or apollo packages in this repo, 
instead you'll find many small "suckless" alternatives to the giants


Structure right now

monorepo
│ 
├── apps
│   ├── dashboard
│   ├── personal
│   └── thrownote
│
├── services
│   ├── css
│   └── fonts
│
├── tools
│   ├── style-packer
│   ├── site-generator 
│   └── git-hooks
│
└── libraries
    ├── color
    ├── http-server
    ├── static-server
    └── stylesheet

---
This list is more of a wishlist in todays state :P

